{
  "texts": [
    "Our study discovered that knowledge application significantly impacts utilitarian value and satisfaction.",
    "On one hand, the utilitarian value appears to be enhanced when users can apply the knowledge acquired from ChatGPT in practical, work-related contexts.",
    "As users effectively apply the knowledge to solve problems, make informed decisions, or improve task efficiency, they perceive a higher value in using the AI system.",
    "This seems consistent with past research, which has emphasized the importance of the practical application of knowledge in improving task performance and perceived utilitarian value 92, 93.",
    "On the other hand, the users' satisfaction with ChatGPT seems to increase when they can effectively apply the knowledge gained from their interactions with the AI."
  ]
}